sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Client as Client Frontend
    participant AS as Authorization Server
    participant RS as Resource Server

    User->>Browser: 1. Initiate payment 650 EUR to Dupont Jean
    Browser->>Client: 2. Forward user action

    Client->>AS: 3. POST /as/par RFC 9126 - authorization_details RAR<br/>type: payment_initiation, amount: 650 EUR, creditorIban: FR7612345600012345678901

    AS-->>Client: 4. { request_uri: urn:...XYZ, expires_in: 60 }

    Client->>Browser: 5. Redirect /authorize?client_id=lbp&request_uri=urn:...XYZ

    Browser->>AS: 6. GET /authorize
    AS->>AS: 7. Retrieve authorization_details from request_uri

    AS->>Browser: 8. Display consent page - Beneficiary: Dupont Jean - IBAN: FR76...8901 - Amount: 650 EUR
    Note over AS,Browser: Displaying payment details BEFORE SCA is mandatory Art.5 RTS DSP2

    AS->>AS: 9. Dynamic Linking: OTP = HMAC(user_key, 65000 || FR7612345600012345678901 || 20240315)
    Note over AS: OTP generated and LINKED to this specific payment BEFORE sending to user

    AS->>User: 10. Send OTP linked to payment details via SMS or push notification

    User->>AS: 11. Submit OTP on consent page

    AS->>AS: 12. Verify: HMAC(user_key, 65000 || FR7612345600012345678901 || 20240315) == submitted OTP
    Note over AS: If amount or IBAN modified - HMAC would not match - payment rejected

    AS-->>Browser: 13. Redirect callback?code=CODE&state=S&iss=https://as.lbp.fr
    Browser->>Client: 14. Return authorization code

    Client->>AS: 15. POST /token { code, code_verifier, DPoP-Proof RFC 9449 }
    AS-->>Client: 16. { access_token DPoP-bound, token_type: DPoP }

    Client->>RS: 17. POST /payments - Authorization: DPoP access_token - Body: { creditorIban, amount, remittanceInfo }

    RS->>RS: 18. Validate DPoP binding - verify authorization_details == body
    RS-->>Client: 19. { paymentId: PAY-2024-LBP-001, status: AcceptedSettlementInProcess }

    Client->>Browser: 20. Display payment confirmation
    Browser-->>User: 21. Payment confirmed - 650 EUR - Loyer Mars 2024

    Note over Client,RS: Token single use - scope payment:initiate one-shot
    Note over AS,Browser: RGPD log consent + timestamp + IP + device
